snippet.title: TakeAglassofwater media
snippet.description:
We will get the Indian call centers shut down.
That's a promise! 

India is a wonderful place with amazing, hard working people.  The people I call in these videos are none of these people. 

This channel is entirely created to post prank phone calls made to scammers that intend to rob people out of their money. 

In the near future, we will be posting many videos of calls where scammers, former scammers, and victims are interviewed. Please stay tuned! 

ps.  Mom..I'm so sorry about the explicit language, extreme rage, and sexual talk in my phone calls. 

Any membership or donation helps the channel as well as helps battle this MS nonsense I am blessed with. Thank you so much to all my patreons! 

Channel started in June 2021 and we are up to 600 subs already!! 

Please spread awareness to people that no company will have you pay with give cards or hook up to your phone or computer. 

These calls hopefully waste a scammers time so a potential victim cannot get through.
